These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, water
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, zinnia, marigold, poppy, dahlia, tulip
7 different games are played: bridge, billiard, monopoly, snooker, canasta, domino, mah-jongg
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 3. the person playing bridge is the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
15. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
16. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
17. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
19. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
20. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Beverage      | fanta    | 7up     | water  | lemonade   | iced-tea | juice      | cola          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| Flower         | bellflower | amaryllis | poppy | dahlia | zinnia   | marigold     | tulip |
| Game     | mah-jongg      | domino   | bridge   | monopoly  | snooker  | canasta | billiard       |

